1
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,399
Dr. Tang.

2
00:01:03,679 --> 00:01:05,159
Do you really think you know Daniel?

3
00:01:06,239 --> 00:01:08,599
You only know you lost your mother ten years ago.

4
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,920
But do you know what he went through that night?

5
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:14,400
The grandma who raised him was dying.

6
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:16,560
And his father

7
00:01:17,359 --> 00:01:19,239
was at your mother's operating table.

8
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,040
Because of your family,

9
00:01:22,159 --> 00:01:22,959
Uncle Jiang missed

10
00:01:23,079 --> 00:01:25,280
the best chance to save his own mother.

11
00:02:43,879 --> 00:02:45,039
Stop torturing yourself.

12
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,560
What's done is done.

13
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,879
There's no going back now.

14
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:52,439
Your mother's spirit in heaven

15
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,159
would never want to see

16
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:55,400
you like this.

17
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:07,319
Daniel.

18
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,719
I wasn't wrong to tell her the truth.

19
00:03:11,919 --> 00:03:12,960
If the two of you

20
00:03:13,319 --> 00:03:14,840
can't even be honest with each other now,

21
00:03:15,199 --> 00:03:16,039
then the road ahead

22
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,520
will only get narrower.

23
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,599
So I should thank you?

24
00:03:20,479 --> 00:03:22,159
For your pathetic vanity

25
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,319
and possessiveness,

26
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:25,240
how far are you willing to go

27
00:03:25,319 --> 00:03:26,120
before you finally stop?

28
00:03:28,199 --> 00:03:29,800
Am I really that despicable in your eyes?

29
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:33,840
Yes.

30
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,240
I can't accept this.

31
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,800
We've known each other since we were seventeen.

32
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,919
Studying, exams,

33
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,000
graduation, work,

34
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,240
which stage of your life

35
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,719
was I not by your side?

36
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,599
Just that one time.

37
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:52,360
I was selfish just once, ten years ago,

38
00:03:52,759 --> 00:03:53,280
and now you want to erase

39
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,879
fifteen years of what we had?

40
00:03:59,319 --> 00:04:00,759
All those years you spent abroad,

41
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:05,280
did you ever dream of Grandma?

42
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:08,560
Even just once?

43
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,680
A woman who loved you as a granddaughter

44
00:04:17,759 --> 00:04:19,959
had just closed her eyes and passed away,

45
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,040
yet for your so-called opportunity,

46
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:23,120
your so-called future,

47
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,680
you turned and left without hesitation.

48
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,720
You didn't even consider

49
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,040
giving her a proper farewell.

50
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:32,240
Lin Fei'er, just admit it.

51
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:34,040
You and Jiang Zhaohe

52
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,319
are essentially the same kind of person.

53
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:38,199
I loved Grandma no less than you did.

54
00:04:41,879 --> 00:04:42,959
But I believe

55
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,240
if you were in my place,

56
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,079
you wouldn't give up your future

57
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,480
for sentimental attachments either.

58
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:48,959
Am I right?

59
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,439
Claude Bernard University Lyon 1.

60
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:59,040
A fellowship in Head and Neck Surgery.

61
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:02,360
I recommended you to Professor Baidi.

62
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,160
He's already agreed.

63
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,040
As long as you're willing,

64
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,600
you can fly to France by month's end.

65
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:10,240
Professor Baidi is chairman of Europe's

66
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,040
Head and Neck Surgery Association.

67
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:13,920
He takes one apprentice every three years.

68
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,519
Do you know how many people

69
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:16,879
dream of an opportunity like this?

70
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:19,279
Don't tell me you're not tempted.

71
00:05:28,839 --> 00:05:30,519
I'll pursue opportunities on my own,

72
00:05:31,839 --> 00:05:32,879
but not right now.

73
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,199
Professor Baidi is nearly seventy.

74
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,160
If you miss this chance,

75
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,879
who knows when another will come.

76
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,519
Jiang Tiancai,

77
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:47,959
where's your ambition?

78
00:05:49,199 --> 00:05:50,480
What about your former dreams?

79
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:52,000
Are you really willing to spend

80
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:53,519
your whole life stuck in this place,

81
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,160
fixing teeth, filling cavities,

82
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,319
wasting your time away?

83
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,920
I want you to think this through carefully.

84
00:06:45,839 --> 00:06:47,879
So you and Dr. Jiang are just over?

85
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:51,439
Could you be any more annoying?

86
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:53,439
She's already a mess inside right now.

87
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,399
Don't make it worse.

88
00:06:54,759 --> 00:06:55,639
Just go, hurry up.

89
00:06:58,079 --> 00:06:59,279
Get going, get going.

90
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:00,319
I'm leaving.

91
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,399
Don't let Lin Fei'er drive you apart.

92
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:12,600
When it comes to relationships,

93
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,160
only the two of you get to decide.

94
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,079
As long as you both think it's worth it,

95
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:18,199
who cares what others say, right?

96
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,759
If only it were that simple.

97
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:24,680
This knot between us,

98
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,959
I'm afraid it can never be undone.

99
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:31,519
Doctor, doctor!

100
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:33,279
Doctor!

101
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:35,279
It hurts so bad, doctor!

102
00:07:35,759 --> 00:07:37,240
Check my wisdom tooth, doctor!

103
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,240
Take a look at this wisdom tooth!

104
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,160
It's killing me!

105
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:42,759
Just yank it out, hurry!

106
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,000
How much have you had to drink?

107
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,360
Extractions aren't advised after drinking.

108
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,680
Not recommended.

109
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:49,240
We can't pull it.

110
00:07:49,279 --> 00:07:50,800
How will I drink with my buddies then?

111
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:52,040
Come on, come on, hurry up!

112
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,000
Just pull it out already!

113
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,800
My buddies are waiting on me for dinner.

114
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:55,600
Sir.

115
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,959
Alcohol impairs coagulation function

116
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:01,879
and affects recovery and anesthesia.

117
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,680
No matter what you say today,

118
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:04,959
I cannot perform the extraction.

119
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:06,720
Let me just examine you first, okay?

120
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:08,519
Alright.

121
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:09,439
Open your mouth.

122
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,639
The position of this wisdom tooth

123
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,720
is tricky, not easy to extract.

124
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,800
How about I give you a painkiller first?

125
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:24,360
After you go home, for 24 hours...

126
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:33,600
Sir!

127
00:08:34,279 --> 00:08:35,039
Tang Yi!

128
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,279
Sir!

129
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,600
Sir!

130
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,000
Somebody help!

131
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,039
Sir, are you okay?

132
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:45,360
Someone help, hurry!

133
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,120
Call 120, quick!

134
00:08:48,639 --> 00:08:49,360
Hurry!

135
00:08:57,559 --> 00:08:58,759
Mom...

136
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,200
Suspected esophageal variceal rupture.

137
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:04,600
Easy now!

138
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:06,039
Call 120, hurry!

139
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,799
Careful!

140
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,039
Tang Yi!

141
00:09:11,279 --> 00:09:12,200
Tang Yi, are you all right?

142
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:13,279
What's wrong?

143
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,559
Medicine... medicine...

144
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,440
Medicine.

145
00:09:15,919 --> 00:09:16,879
What medicine?

146
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,320
Where is it?

147
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,559
Medicine.

148
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:25,279
Medicine.

149
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,320
What medicine?

150
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:36,720
Tang Yi, Tang Yi!

151
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:39,480
Tang Yi, Tang Yi!

152
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:40,480
How is she?

153
00:09:40,879 --> 00:09:41,440
Suction!

154
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:42,559
Get the suction, hurry!

155
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,600
Move aside!

156
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:51,399
What happened to her?

157
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,120
It's okay, it's okay.

158
00:10:06,159 --> 00:10:06,879
Tang Yi.

159
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:16,559
Tang Yi.

160
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,200
It's all right.

161
00:10:25,919 --> 00:10:26,639
It's all right.

162
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:32,120
It's over now, it's over.

163
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,799
There's no way we're breaking up.

164
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:38,600
Not in this lifetime.

165
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:53,720
It's all right.

166
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,559
Don't move.

167
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,559
Let me hold you a little longer.

168
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,759
Thank you, Jiang Tiancai.

169
00:12:14,279 --> 00:12:16,159
Thank you for coming into my life.

170
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:20,200
Thank you for saving me,

171
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,480
again and again, without hesitation.

172
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,559
Remember this,

173
00:12:36,159 --> 00:12:37,200
I'm not Jiang Zhaohe,

174
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,480
and you're not your mother.

175
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,639
I don't care what happened before.

176
00:12:43,159 --> 00:12:44,399
But from now on,

177
00:12:45,679 --> 00:12:46,720
you're not alone anymore.

178
00:12:49,039 --> 00:12:49,799
Since you once

179
00:12:49,879 --> 00:12:51,720
pulled me out of the darkness,

180
00:12:52,879 --> 00:12:54,200
I'll never abandon you.

181
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:10,080
Then, Dr. Jiang,

182
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:11,960
from now on,

183
00:13:13,399 --> 00:13:14,559
please take good care of me.

184
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:32,159
Our deputy director spot is still open.

185
00:14:32,399 --> 00:14:33,879
Is Director Zeng considering Dr. Jiang?

186
00:14:34,399 --> 00:14:35,840
By seniority or by ability,

187
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,440
it should be Dr. Chen's turn, right?

188
00:14:37,679 --> 00:14:39,200
He's Director Zeng's direct protégé.

189
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:41,879
If Director Zeng really had that in mind,

190
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,200
he would've announced it long ago.

191
00:14:43,519 --> 00:14:44,679
Look how much time has passed,

192
00:14:44,759 --> 00:14:45,720
and not a single word.

193
00:14:46,399 --> 00:14:47,440
On the surface, Director Zeng demoted Dr. Jiang

194
00:14:47,519 --> 00:14:48,440
to General Dentistry,

195
00:14:48,799 --> 00:14:50,480
but secretly he's grooming him,

196
00:14:50,799 --> 00:14:52,279
preparing him to surpass everyone else.

197
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:54,240
You can't tell me you didn't consider

198
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:56,159
the risk of facial nerve injury too.

199
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:57,759
You two, switch places.

200
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:58,840
Continue the surgery.

201
00:15:02,159 --> 00:15:03,120
But this was clearly Dr. Chen's

202
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,320
plan to begin with.

203
00:15:06,159 --> 00:15:07,039
Dr. Chen.

204
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:11,799
Jiang Tiancai.

205
00:15:12,679 --> 00:15:14,320
You forced me into this.

206
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:26,120
Dr. Jiang.

207
00:15:26,919 --> 00:15:27,919
There are photos.

208
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,440
He hit someone!

209
00:15:29,559 --> 00:15:30,840
Look, isn't that him?

210
00:15:31,399 --> 00:15:32,759
Yes, yes, that's him.

211
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,399
If you're gonna date, date a male doctor

212
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:40,919
who can bond with kids like that.

213
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:43,360
We're at work. Stop being so mushy.

214
00:15:43,679 --> 00:15:45,320
Fired from Pingjin First Hospital for

215
00:15:45,399 --> 00:15:47,440
assault, that unscrupulous Dr. Jiang

216
00:15:47,679 --> 00:15:48,799
has miraculously transformed

217
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:51,039
into a rising star at a dental hospital

218
00:15:51,159 --> 00:15:52,960
on the southeast coast.

219
00:15:59,759 --> 00:16:01,240
It's him! That's him!

220
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:03,200
Jiang Tiancai has no medical ethics!

221
00:16:03,279 --> 00:16:03,960
Unscrupulous doctor!

222
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:06,480
What are you doing?

223
00:16:06,759 --> 00:16:08,879
And this guy's still a doctor?

224
00:16:19,639 --> 00:16:22,080
Wisdom teeth are lucky teeth. Don't pull them if you can avoid it.

225
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:23,559
Don't be fooled!

226
00:16:24,039 --> 00:16:25,840
Recurring wisdom tooth decay and swelling,

227
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:27,879
food debris always stuck while brushing,

228
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,480
half-erupted and stalled,

229
00:16:29,679 --> 00:16:31,039
overgrown and extended,

230
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:32,600
or causing damage to adjacent teeth.

231
00:16:32,919 --> 00:16:34,320
If you encounter any of these,

232
00:16:34,559 --> 00:16:36,360
pull, pull, pull them out promptly!

233
00:16:36,559 --> 00:16:37,840
Don't let a small issue cause big trouble!

